{"id":1364,"date":"2018-12-12T13:23:00","date_gmt":"2018-12-12T18:23:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1364"},"modified":"2023-07-26T15:24:04","modified_gmt":"2023-07-26T19:24:04","slug":"jonathan-ruel","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/jonathan-ruel\/","title":{"rendered":"Jonathan Ruel"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"p1\">Jonathan d\u00e9tient un baccalaur\u00e9at en math\u00e9matiques et physique de l\u2019Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al, de m\u00eame qu\u2019une ma\u00eetrise et un doctorat en physique de l\u2019universit\u00e9 Harvard. \u00c9crivain \u00e0 ses heures, il a publi\u00e9 un roman (<em>L\u2019astronome dur \u00e0 cuire<\/em>, \u00c9ditions Druide). Vous le trouverez peut-\u00eatre un peu trop enthousiaste \u00e0 propos de la physique th\u00e9orique, du travail de laboratoire, de l&rsquo;astronomie, du travail en coll\u00e9gialit\u00e9, de la rigueur, des livres et du petit matin.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1365,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[2270,297],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1364","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-sciences-de-la-nature","departement-equipe-physique"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1364","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1365"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1364"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"c